    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Entropy Centre 是一款烧脑的解谜冒险游戏，你需要通过回溯时间来揭示物体本来的样子，从而攻克看似不可能的障碍和难题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730590/extras/48ae9c00a8669eee5f46a636821fd1f6.poster.avif?t=1759166404\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730590/extras/48ae9c00a8669eee5f46a636821fd1f6.webm?t=1759166404\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730590/extras/48ae9c00a8669eee5f46a636821fd1f6.mp4?t=1759166404\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随心操纵时间并巧妙破解极具挑战性的谜题房间，而每次破解都会让你更接近地球轨道上的巨型空间站核心。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730590/extras/284f2d574d95afcbaccea06bf0cdcbfd.poster.avif?t=1759166404\" width=780 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730590/extras/284f2d574d95afcbaccea06bf0cdcbfd.webm?t=1759166404\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730590/extras/284f2d574d95afcbaccea06bf0cdcbfd.mp4?t=1759166404\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因为一场毁天灭地的事件，整个世界都陷入了熊熊烈火，似乎只有你一个人活了下来。人类的唯一希望就在 The Entropy Centre 的核心位置。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730590/extras/1832f06f6f87713e5368219d25b6131a.poster.avif?t=1759166404\" width=780 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730590/extras/1832f06f6f87713e5368219d25b6131a.webm?t=1759166404\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730590/extras/1832f06f6f87713e5368219d25b6131a.mp4?t=1759166404\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >认识一下由 The Entropy Centre 最尖端技术打造的杰作 ASTRA 吧。ASTRA 是一件由人工智能驱动的设备，它能够扫描物体的时空顺序，并将其回溯至过去。它的功能包括复原倒塌的柱子和重新加热冷掉的茶。怎么样，很酷吧？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730590/extras/135d6a217b1880da1331a140f230fc24.poster.avif?t=1759166404\" width=780 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730590/extras/135d6a217b1880da1331a140f230fc24.webm?t=1759166404\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730590/extras/135d6a217b1880da1331a140f230fc24.mp4?t=1759166404\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Entropy Centre 的瓦解、地球的灭亡... 一切的真相都能够在这杂乱而危险的设施中心找到。但你会接受等待着你的不幸事实吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730590/extras/45b4b97e7f1855799af466a3dec16ca1.poster.avif?t=1759166404\" width=780 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730590/extras/45b4b97e7f1855799af466a3dec16ca1.webm?t=1759166404\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730590/extras/45b4b97e7f1855799af466a3dec16ca1.mp4?t=1759166404\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >凭借犀利幽默的剧情和杰出的配音表演，The Entropy Centre 完美地将烧脑的解谜和史诗般的冒险融合在了一起。</p>",
